    <h>simple verbs</h>
    <p>Simple verbs are <a href="?xx=verbs/verbs">verbs</a> that are not formed out of other
        words.</p>
    <p>Simple verbs contrast with <!--<a href="?xx=verbs/derived_verbs">-->derived verbs<!--</a>-->
        and <!--<a href="?xx=verbs/compound_verbs">-->compound verbs<!--</a>--> which
            <emph>are</emph> formed out of other words.</p>

    <section id="irregular">
        <h>irregular verbs</h>
        <p>List of irregular verbs – <ul>
                <li><a href="?gd=bi"><g>bi</g></a>
                    <en>be</en></li>
                <li><a href="?gd=deean"><g>dèan</g></a>
                    <en>do, make</en></li>
                <li><a href="?gd=faic"><g>faic</g></a>
                    <en>see</en></li>
                <!--<li><a href="?gd=rach"><g>rach</g></a>
                <en>go</en></li>
